p.d: In disagreement about the L'Arquebuse, will MeI and Chang accept Vapali's unexpected offer? Odile and Alexandre face a dilemma: should they reveal the secret of Claudine's past? Clément has an emotional encounter with an old acquaintance that shakes his convictions... Directed by: Philippe Lefebvre (France, 2019) Screenplay: Diane Clavier, Samantha Mazeras Cast: Fred Testot (Serge), Armelle Chahbi (Anissa), Linh-Dan Pham (MeI), Maurice Cheng (Chang), Constance Dollé (Odile), Philippe Lefebvre (Alexandre), Éva Darlan (Claudine), Jonathan Lambert (Clément), Éléna Plonka (Brune), Cassiopée Mayance (Anouk), Alexis Baudry (Jean-Paul), Luna Lou (Violette), Achille Potier (Armand), Nicolas Lecolley (Matthieu), François Vincentelli (Arnaud Vapali) Genre: comedy
